ruby-cairo
------------------------------------------
Ruby bindings for the cairo graphics engine.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.21-2
  libcairo2-1.2.4-1
  ruby-1.8.4-1

Build requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.21-2
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.2.6-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-1
  make-3.81-1
  pkg-config-0.20-1
  ruby-1.8.4-1
  libcairo-devel-1.2.4-1

Canonical website:
  http://cairographics.org/

Canonical download:
  http://cairographics.org/releases/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ruby-cairo-1.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ruby-cairo-1.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ruby-cairo-1.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ruby-cairo-1.2.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/cairo.rb
  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/cairo.so
  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/libruby-cairo.a
  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/rb_cairo.h
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ruby-cairo-1.2.0.README
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-cairo-1.2.0/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-cairo-1.2.0/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-cairo-1.2.0/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-cairo-1.2.0/GPL
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-cairo-1.2.0/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-cairo-1.2.0/README

------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.2.0-1 -----
Version bump.  Changed package name from rcairo for consistency with 
the ruby-gnome2 packages.

----- version 1.0.0-2 -----
Include link library in binary package for ruby-gnome2 cairo support.

----- version 1.0.0-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


